Class SalariedProgrammer

java.lang.Object
Programmer
SalariedProgrammer
All Implemented Interfaces:
Payme
public class SalariedProgrammer extends Programmer
SalariedProgrammer concrete class extends abstract class Programmer. It's subclass inheriting the firstName, lastName, socialSecurityNumber variables and the toString and getPaymentAmount methods, with its own private data member WeeklySalary and setWeeklySalary and getWeeklySalary methods
